 What Where Find Jobs Advanced Job Search Saviynt Administrator Capgemini 8,227 reviews Remote Remote Capgemini 8,227 reviews Read what people are saying about working here. Job details Job Type Contract Full Job Description Duration : 12+ months 
Responsibilities/Requirements: 
Perform custom development against a Saviynt Identity and Access Management (IAM) system to enable it to read user and group information from a customer-provided database and then generate that information into the Saviynt system for use in maintaining users and groups in target enterprise directories. 
5-8 years of experience 
Saviynt IAM system and custom module development 
Lightweight Directory Access Protocol (LDAP) directories, including Microsoft Active Directory 
Azure Active Directory and Google Cloud IAM 
Programming languages, including Java 
Database protocols, including ODBC, JDBC, and Structured Query Language (SQL) 
Handling all basic administrative functions including user account maintenance, reports and dashboards, workflows, and other routine tasks 
Administering regular internal system audits and prepared for upgrades 
Coordinating the evaluation, scope, and completion of new development requests 
Working independently with members of the user community to define and document development requirements 
Using of productivity and analysis tools to manage iterative delivery: JIRA, Google Analytics, Git Repository, MS TEAMS, Confluence 
Practical ITIL knowledge and experience 
